data.description: Welcome to your Hill Country homestead! This property has so much to offer. The 3-bedroom 2-bathroom home boast a spacious kitchen that overlooks great porch. With a relaxing living room. Natural light pierces through the home from the abundance of windows. Perfect place to get back to country living while still being close to town. Lots of upgrades and very welcoming. Enjoy the outside while sitting around the spacious porch and enjoying all the wildlife. Almost end-of-road for country quiet. Upgrades include new windows, new garage door, remodeled master bath, new paint, new landscape, new fence, new doors, Car port, storage building and much more. Agent Remarks: See list of Upgrades & Updates in Documents. Directions: Take Ranchero to Michon or clear view then left on mountain drive and left on Heather
